data.description: Come tour this beautiful home built in 2013 and MOVE IN READY!! 3 bed + Study - could be used as 4th bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage in a quiet neighborhood and LESS than 1 mile to Presidio Town Shopping Center at Alliance! Large open concept floor plan with BRAND NEW carpet throughout, granite countertops, large island overlooking living area, plenty of storage, stainless steel appliances, walk in pantry, eat in breakfast area, large covered porches, WBFP, 2in blinds throughout, upgraded lighting package, oversized master shower, WIC, double sinks, and more!
